M'tsolola
Comoros

INGREDIENTS

Fish
Onion
Tomato
Cumin
Chili Powder
Turmeric
Coriander
Cardamom
Coconut milk


MISE

Cut plantains
Cut Cassava
Chop onion
Chop Tomato
Show Fish
Wash Plantains & Cassava


COOK

Cook Plantains & Cassava
Fry Fish
Add to pot
Add onion
Add Tomato
Add Spices
Add Water
Add Coconut Milk
Simmer fish fpr 20min
Add plantains
Simmer for 10min
Sprinkle with lemon
Serve